description: NOLA Girl Food Truck & Catering is dedicated utilizing fresh and local ingredients including Louisiana seafood, Louisiana products and fresh market produce as much as possible in order to create and re-create some of the best and most celebrated dishes enjoyed by local New Orleanians and visitors alike.     We offer gourmet street food with a menu that ranges from classic New Orleans, to NOLA Fusion to Southern American.  Some of our dishes include BBQ Shrimp Pasta, Brisket Quesadilla, Root Beer Braised Pull Pork Po’ Boy, Grilled Chicken Cordon Bleu Sliders, Boudin Pot Stickers and Crawfish Fried Rice (seasonal) to name a few.  Let NOLA Girl Food Truck & Catering cater your next function! We offer catering options for all types of events from private parties, business meetings and wedding receptions to private dinner parties for smaller groups and private dinners for couples.
name: NOLA Girl Catering & Food Truck
